{"tid":2453213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂喂喂浸大要人投票啊！今日八點完啦！！","createTime":"2021-03-19T10:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T10:38:33.000Z","uid":208530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"709e785e4ee139839a5c3ebd2603e7102566d946","tid":2453213,"uid":208530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"【周年大選補選】第四日投票率達6.38%<br />\n<br />\n【浸大編委訊】第五十三屆周年大選補選普選評議員選舉（第六類別）投票，於3月15日起一連五日進行。鑑於武漢肺炎疫症持續，是次大選將繼續網上投票，會員須登入系統投票。截止3月18日晚上9時30分，共有751人投票，累積投票率為6.38%，遠低於第五十一屆周年大選補選的11.67%，但比上屆周年大選補選的5.9%稍高。<br />\n<br />\n投票期將於明晚八時結束。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n網上投票連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://edmsys.hkbu.edu.hk/tracker/URLServer/91155431/9xVhgwfid8R6tQn3eIMNR9EY/38568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedmsys.hkbu.edu.hk%2Ftracker%2FURLServer%2F91155431%2F9xVhgwfid8R6tQn3eIMNR9EY%2F38568&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=d015eabd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edmsys.hkbu.edu.hk/tracker/URLServer/91155431/9xVhgwfid8R6tQn3eIMNR9EY/38568</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMkDyNulrLH/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMkDyNulrLH%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=75a16e3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMkDyNulrLH%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&h=759f67e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CMkDyNulrLH/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">喂阿哥，撳個掣姐，快啲投啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e279daa90f090e2c63047c4d9a2de398280872b2","tid":2453213,"uid":208530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl